<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        console.log("üéÅ Iniciando animaciones de sugerencia de regalo...");

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê T√çTULO "SUGERENCIA DE REGALO" ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            "#titulo-regalo",
            { opacity: 0, y: -30 },
            {
                opacity: 1,
                y: 0,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "power2.out",
                scrollTrigger: {
                    trigger: "#titulo-regalo",
                    start: "top 80%",
                    once: true
                }
            }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê TEXTO EXPLICATIVO ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            "#texto-explicativo",
            { opacity: 0, y: 20 },
            {
                opacity: 1,
                y: 0,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "power2.out",
                scrollTrigger: {
                    trigger: "#texto-explicativo",
                    start: "top 80%",
                    once: true
                },
                delay: 0.3
            }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê TARJETA DE SOBRE ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            "#tarjeta-sobre",
            { opacity: 0, x: -50, scale: 0.9 },
            {
                opacity: 1,
                x: 0,
                scale: 1,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "back.out(1.4)",
                scrollTrigger: {
                    trigger: "#tarjeta-sobre",
                    start: "top 80%",
                    once: true
                },
                delay: 0.5
            }
        );

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê TARJETA DE QR ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.fromTo(
            "#tarjeta-qr",
            { opacity: 0, x: 50, scale: 0.9 },
            {
                opacity: 1,
                x: 0,
                scale: 1,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "back.out(1.4)",
                scrollTrigger: {
                    trigger: "#tarjeta-qr",
                    start: "top 80%",
                    once: true
                },
                delay: 0.7
            }
        );

        console.log("‚ú® Animaciones de sugerencia de regalo completadas!");
    });
</script>

<style>
    /* Transiciones suaves en las tarjetas */
    #tarjeta-sobre,
    #tarjeta-qr {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    #tarjeta-sobre:hover,
    #tarjeta-qr:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* Efecto hover en el t√≠tulo */
    #titulo-regalo:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
</style>